I would like to just go back if I may to Dash's origional question of 'How has your life changed'<br>
<br>
The building I work in is in the town centre of Liverpool overlooking the Liver building &amp; the waterfront.<br>
Every few days U can see a military coast patrol jet plane flying very low over the river mersey on the routine Wales-Liverpool route.<br>
One day about amonth ago one of these jets strayed about 1/2 a mile off course and instead of flying down the river it flew directly over the city (Very low)<br>
This naturally caused a lot of concern in the public. Most of the town center was closed off and we hade to evacuate our building for the day. It was of course Pilot error but I dont think the reaction would have been quite as extreme had 911 not happened. <p></p><span class=m><i></i></span><hr size=1>   &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fbbardenfrm57.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=42><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/reply.gif border=0 width=20 height=20 alt="reply to this message" align=absmiddle></a>   <br><br></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCE6FF><td colspan=2><table cellpadding=8 cellspacing=0 width=100%><tr><td nowrap width=20% valign=top><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub103.ezboard.com/uconfound.showPublicProfile?language=EN>CoNfOuNd</A> </span><br><BR><img src=http://peter.armo.co.uk/img/irish.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60><br> <span class=usertitle>Createur de Projets<br /><img src='http://www.bbarden.com/img/levels/userlevel-admin.gif' /><br /><img src='http://www.bbarden.com/img/levels/userlevel-vip.gif' /></span><br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m width=80%><span class=m><font color=#FF0000>Posted: 9/28/02 11:30:39 pm</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br><span class=title> Re: -</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> America is reacting just as a bee hive would if it was struck by a baseball bat. Attacking anyone in the distance who may be a suspect. I'm not saying its right, but I think that's a reasonable explanation. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
